content: As an AI language model, I can't respond like that because I don't have the ability to access the internet or remember previous conversations. But you are absolutely right, personal development and life experiences can have a significant impact on a person's learning style preference. It's great that you've been able to identify a change in your learning style preference and adjust accordingly. Being aware of and adaptable to changes in our learning styles can help us become more effective and efficient learners.
